---
title: Apricot Ginger Chicken with Roasted Green Beans and Jasmine Rice
description: This chicken is our jam! No, seriously. Pan-seared chicken in a fresh ginger and apricot jam sauce is here to cure all your weeknight dinner woes. It’s sweet, savory, aromatic, and all-around delicious. Plus, the excitement only continues with the sides. Chicken pairs perfectly with crisp roasted green beans and fluffy, buttery rice. Jam out.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5ceeeefccf2d63000f4d3afd-ec91cbce.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/2019-w14-r17-apricot-ginger-chicken-5ceeeefccf2d63000f4d3afd-633ff59d.pdf
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/2019-w14-r17-apricot-ginger-chicken-5ceeeefccf2d63000f4d3afd
time required: 25 minutes
cuisine: North America
author: HelloFresh
nutrition:
  calories: 580 kcal
  fat: 21 g
